Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的第18个夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对身为重考生的我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是不是夏天都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次等重要的还是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成绩一直都没什么进步耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别那么沮丧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个夏天努力用功的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋天就一定能看到成果的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为夏天是关键时刻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，本须和，加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件泳装你觉得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是为了今天而买的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很…很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常合适
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是个大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，ちぃ衣服換好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的到海边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是个重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的能待在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模拟考成绩拿 D 的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贫穷又无暇的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，本须和，加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，周末海边见罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保应该已经跟你说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三天两夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定也会去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又没那个钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国分寺他说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每年的这个时候\N都会到海边的别墅去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我们要跟他一起同行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以是免费的喔，免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,免费…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不过我们可是重考生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能去海边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ泳裝穿這件好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的旧衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理员小姐我也邀请了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有，那女孩叫裕美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都说要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，本须和先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克服夏天考验吧，重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是电脑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，跟裕美\N還有清水老師打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是中午吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用白天的打招呼法，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，ちぃ真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还要杵在那里多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游玩的时间会被耗光的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去帮帮本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，这里就叫作“海”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要不要一起去玩水？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的海域\N深度不均匀，要小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直像是小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么难得的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好好享受怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呸，好…好咸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你要东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海水是鹹的，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咸水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了\N电脑碰到盐水不会有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电脑都有做日常防水\N所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊，说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长对电脑也很温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢泼我水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起游到那里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不勉强你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我可不会让你溜掉的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚…晚上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你上特别课程
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会有间别墅在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你家果然真有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是那个对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的私人海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是没人来这里玩罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，检测结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会不会打扰到你们了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家吵吵闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实是有点吵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的确比较热闹呢\N稔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过偶而这样也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都到了这里，不需要看书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来玩吧！来玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:09:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去囉，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,球，秀树给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的幸福应该就是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不错的转换心情方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我可没忘记要用功喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经打算今夏要\N从早到晚苦读了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着来玩扑克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得清水老师的房间应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我会帮你上特别课程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的课程是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一段夏季的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门没锁，请进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人缺席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也拿去抹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电脑用的防腐蚀膏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:13:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为海风、盐水跟沙粒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都算是精密仪器的天敌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好还是抹一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，不是有日常防水了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是帮她保养一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,均匀的涂抹在全身就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,均匀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我抹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫ちぃ抹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3、2、1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,办…办不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我怎么办得到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就教她自己涂抹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先将防护膏像这样挤出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和先生\N要不要我来帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那是貝類，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝类，那这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，那也是贝类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝类，这也是贝类吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会走的贝类？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，这个叫什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是寄居蟹啦，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喔对喔，叫寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那叫寄居蟹喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在教她词句吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ現在還有很多事不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果不教她的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昆布吗？\N不，是裙带菜吗？还是海藻？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫海草不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海草，那是海草，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是海草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我也来帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，拜…拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是海豚耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海…海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚，是海豚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳的眼力真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有海豚耶，海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们偶而会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊，这不是很棒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只在电视上看过海豚耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也只在水族馆看过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，这里也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点远\N不过真的有看到对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能近一点看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会不会游到这附近来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到近，如果游到这种近海来\N不就回不去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过很少有这种机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真想多看一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就游到外面一点去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该没多远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学…学长，难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你说不会游泳\N不是开玩笑的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我干嘛拿这个来开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹也会蛙式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任谁都有擅长\N与不擅长的东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊，学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很好吗，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联考不考游泳这科目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树不会游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样很厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树很厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私人游艇耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然觉得有点火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这世界这样真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会很不公平吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要观赏海豚\N这一带是最佳地点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那个你有看到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树看到海豚的“哗啦”\N会很高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也要來嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和，还不快去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，反正她有日常防水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么深的地方\N日常防水一点用也没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不会游泳吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国分寺的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，学长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这么乱来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊，不经思索就跳下去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真像你的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:20:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从表面看来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也没进水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，你在生气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ做錯事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会生气呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真是台不可思议的电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般如果掉到海里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会进水，然后会很难修复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果ちぃ發生事情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许会变得更麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救本須和起來的可是ちぃ喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2、2…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的夏天结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.42,0:22:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次等重要的还是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个夏天是关键时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标是成绩进步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成绩竟然又退步了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，夏天热吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，夏天真热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:24:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个人昏沉沉的，一点精神都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.10,0:24:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天要用蚊香吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蚊香的味道\N可说是夏天的必需品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.28,0:24:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天清水老师会来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，没错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.25,0:24:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天还是清水老师最棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，招待」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.99,0:24:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乐意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.09,0:24:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乐意之至

